# Code Review Checklist

This checklist defines what constitutes a "Critical" code review failure.

## Critical Checks (Blocking)

### Security & Auth
{{#if hasAuth}}
- Are protected routes properly guarded?
- Is the user ID extracted from a trusted token, not client input?
{{/if}}
- Is PII logged?

### Data Layer ({{orm}})
{{#if hasPrisma}}
- Does the migration drop data without a backfill?
- Are missing unique constraints applied?
{{else if hasTypeORM}}
- Are `@Transaction()` decorators used correctly?
- Did migrations get generated properly without data loss?
{{/if}}

### Architecture ({{framework}})
{{#if isNestJS}}
- Are services bleeding into controllers?
- Is DI configured correctly (no manual `new Service()` calls)?
{{else}}
- Are routers properly encapsulated?
- Are error handlers catching async rejections?
{{/if}}

